---
source: crates/mineral-tui/src/runtime/keymap.rs
description: "默认键位绑定表(和弦 → 动作,字典序;default.lua keys/behavior 落地产物)"
expression: "lines.join(\"\\n\")"
---
+ → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(5))
- → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(-5))
/ → EnterSearch
<BS> → BackOrClearSearch
<C-b> → Scroll(PageUp)
<C-d> → Scroll(LineDown)
<C-f> → Scroll(PageDown)
<C-u> → Scroll(LineUp)
<CR> → ActivateSelection
<Down> → MoveSelection(Down(1))
<Esc> → BackOrClearSearch
<Left> → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(-5))
<Right> → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(5))
<S-Left> → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(-30))
<S-Right> → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(30))
<Space> → TogglePlayPause
<Tab> → OpenQueue
<Up> → MoveSelection(Up(1))
= → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(5))
G → MoveSelection(Last)
J → MoveSelection(Down(7))
K → MoveSelection(Up(7))
_ → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(-5))
d → DownloadSelection
f → ToggleLoveSelection
g → MoveSelection(First)
h → BackOrClearSearch
j → MoveSelection(Down(1))
k → MoveSelection(Up(1))
l → ActivateSelection
m → CyclePlayMode
n → NextSong
o → OpenActionMenu
p → PrevOrRestart
q → OpenQuitConfirm
s → OpenSearchView
t → CycleLyricExtra
x → DismissNotice
y → OpenCopyMenu
z → ToggleFullscreen
